  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This spell will cause another mob to run away for a certain amount of time. It can save you butt when you cannot handle the mob, which it will allow you to gate/ run before he comes back.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
